# MVP of Employee Termination Prediction
In this folder, the Minimum Viable Product (MVP) is provided.
The initial steps in detail are provided in the Jupyter notebook. 

# The MVP notebook summarizes the following: 
1- Explore the features
2- Drop unnecessary coloumns
3- Drop all columns not available before termination
4- Split df into X and Y
5- Train - test split

# There are one more step to finish the project:
Use different machine learning algorithm like random forest, knn, ...
